docs.text: Yu-Gi-Oh! Commands /card <name> Get card info. The name doesn't have to be precise, for example adhara will match Tenyi Spirit - Adhara . /price <name> Get price info of a card. This will give prices from TCGPlayer, CardMarket, eBay along with a small breakdown for different sets. The name doesn't have to be precise, for example adhara will match Tenyi Spirit - Adhara .
